prompts.prompt: A high-contrast, gritty street portrait of a man, late 20s, in front of a heavily textured, paint-peeling wall in an old neighborhood. Shot with a vintage film camera aesthetic, heavy grain and subtle color shift.
A glitch-art style headshot of a young man with a neutral pose, where digital static and neon geometric lines are subtly overlaid on the image, blending modern tech aesthetics with his face.
A low-key portrait (mostly dark tones) of an Indian musician (30s) with long hair, illuminated only by a single warm spotlight from above. Holding a guitar neck partially in the frame.
A hyper-realistic close-up of an Indian actor. Focus on the eyes, which are intense and direct. Shot with a wide-aperture lens against a completely out-of-focus, colorful background.
A cinematic headshot of an Indian man, mid-40s, with a serious expression. Dramatic chiaroscuro lighting, half his face in deep shadow and half intensely lit. Inspired by Caravaggio paintings.
A 'candid' moment of a man in a cafe, looking away from the camera, smiling slightly while holding a coffee cup. Warm, tungsten lighting, soft focus.
A photorealistic portrait of an Indian man with stylishly groomed hair and a simple grey hoodie, shot in soft, diffused evening light. Neutral expression, very high detail on hair strands.
A close-up headshot of a male fitness trainer, early 30s, short-cropped hair, wearing athletic wear. Sweat glistening slightly on his forehead. Against a dark, textured gym wall.
A travel blogger (20s) with a light beard, wearing a denim jacket. Smiling genuinely, facing a jungle or mountain backdrop (like the Himalayas). Bright, sunny daylight.

A casual, relaxed headshot of a man in a simple black t-shirt. Shot in an outdoor urban setting, like a busy street market in Delhi, but with the man sharply in focus and the background blurred (bokeh).
A portrait of a young artist from Kolkata wearing a simple cotton kurta, sitting with a cup of chai. Subtle, moody lighting filtering through a window pane. Extremely realistic skin texture.
A high-fashion, monochrome portrait of a modern man in a sophisticated black Bandhgala suit. Focus on the intricate texture of the fabric. Intense, direct gaze against a plain dark wall.

A candid portrait of an elderly Rajasthani gentleman with a distinguished mustache, wearing a vibrant, patterned turban. Deeply wrinkled face conveying wisdom. Shot with dramatic natural light, highly textured.
A close-up portrait of a South Indian groom (20s) wearing a traditional silk wedding dhoti and an ornate gold thread shawl (angavastram). Shot with soft, warm light in a temple courtyard.
A striking headshot of a Punjabi man in his late 20s wearing a crisp, ivory white kurta and a light saffron turban (pagdi). Shot outdoors during the Golden Hour, deep saturation.
A corporate headshot of a middle-aged, distinguished man, salt-and-pepper hair, in a classic pinstripe suit. Subtle catchlight in the eyes. Shot with a medium-format lens for extreme detail.
A Mumbai-based entrepreneur (30s) wearing a well-fitted light grey Nehru jacket over a white kurta. Clean, white studio background. Professional, approachable smile.
A mid-career Indian financial analyst (40s) in a charcoal grey suit. Shot in black and white, with dramatic, cinematic lighting. Slight furrow in the brow, conveying seriousness and expertise.

A young Indian software engineer in a light blue collared shirt and modern wire-frame glasses. Against a blurred, minimalist office background. Natural, window-side lighting, close-up, high-resolution photo.

A 35-year-old successful South Indian CEO in a tailored dark navy suit, seated at a mahogany desk. Gazing directly at the camera with a confident, open smile. Soft studio lighting. Depth of field effect.
